com.camerontec.catalys.server.configuration.xmlconverter

Class XMLConfigurationReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.configuration.xmlconverter.XMLConfigurationReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConfigurationReader

    public class XMLConfigurationReader
extends Object
implements IConfigurationReader
    Configuration reader that uses XML as a source of configuration. Loads the XML configuration file into a registry as IMutableConfiguration objects.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors

      XMLConfigurationReader(String configFileName, ConfigurationObjectRegistry registry, boolean xmlValidation, String clusterNodeId)
      Create an XML Configuration reader, which will read the XML configuration specified by configFileName/applicationID into the supplied configuration registry.
      XMLConfigurationReader(String configFileName, ConfigurationObjectRegistry registry, String clusterNodeId)
      Create an XML Configuration reader, which will read the XML configuration specified by configFileName/applicationID into the supplied configuration registry.
      The XML file will be validated against the DTD/Schema when parsed.
